column5: Looking for someone to build a custom rod....any recommendations???
Try Backwoods Preimium Rods out of Wasaga Beach in Ontario, They have a web site www.backwoodsrods.com
You can try this site to locate a builder close to your location.http://www.tackleworks.org/ Good luck, Brad
